Art, yeah I know DocDel is sick, I advised him to go inpatient and get some alchol rub downs from the angels in white....assuming politically correctness and gender applies.<br><br>
You are more than welcome to nail me to the barn door, and I will return the favor in spades, should the opportuity arise. Count on it.<br><br>
How nice it is, however, that we have just connected in peace, after 30 years of anger and rage, and of unknowing each other.  That makes me feel about 20 feel tall and will send me off to bed grinning like a loney.  (appropriate for a shrink I guess). One thing. Don't let my occupation put you off.  What I don't check at the door is long burned out. I am mostly out of the active shrink game these days, more a war story teller and paper pusher.  And you pushed a mightly good push, and I do appreciate it.   Welcome home to both of us, eh?<br><br>
